function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	--Hydra.TraceScreen("Ambush Start event received")
	if (#Hydra.ActorsInGroup(DEMON_AMBUSH_TRIGGERS_AND_SPAWNERS) > 0) then
		for i, idAmbushActor in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup(DEMON_AMBUSH_TRIGGERS_AND_SPAWNERS)) do
			--Hydra.TraceScreen("Enabling: ", idAmbushActor)
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idAmbushActor)
			if Hydra.ActorGizmoIsDisabled(idAmbushActor) then
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idAmbushActor, false)
			end
		end
	end
end
